A former governor of Borno State, Ali Modu Sheriff, has paid a visit to the National Secretariat of the All Progressives Congress in Abuja ahead of the National Convention of the party.Sherrif arrived the secretariat at about 4:00pm on Thursday but declined to speak to journalists on his mission to the APC complex.Â 

